snippet: A 19-year-old biracial man who was unarmed when he was killed by a white Madison police officer was shot in his head, right arm and torso, according to preliminary autopsy reports released Friday.
abstract: Autopsy report on Tony Robinson, unarmed 19-year-old biracial man who was killed by white Madison, Wis, Police Officer Matt Kenny, reveals that he died from multiple gun shot wounds.
lead_paragraph: A 19-year-old biracial man who was unarmed when he was killed by a white Madison police officer was shot in his head, right arm and torso, according to preliminary autopsy reports released Friday.

headline.main: Wisconsin: Autopsy Released in Man’s Killing by Police
